  "remarks": "Alexandru Beșchieru is the leader of the “Forța de Alternativă și de Salvare a Moldovei” (“FASM”) political party, which is one of the successors of the outlawed ȘOR political party, led by Ilan Shor. In April 2024, Ilan Shor launched in Moscow the Victory/Pobeda Political Bloc, which unites the successors of his party, including FASM.",
